This paper deals with style transfer, which is a popular topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The paper also discusses texture synthesis, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM). The use of gram matrices and hyper-parameters suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
